    <item>
      <title>津巴布韦总统称，2030 年前津巴布韦可能会采用 ZiG 作为唯一货币</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/zimbabwe-president-hints-at-sole-use-of-zig-before-2030-usd-zwg</link>
      <description><![CDATA[津巴布韦总统埃默森·姆南加古瓦暗示，在 2030 年结束现行多货币体系的最后期限之前，该国新的以金银为支撑的货币将成为唯一的法定货币。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/zimbabwe-president-hints-at-sole-use-of-zig-before-2030-usd-zwg</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 21:49:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英镑保持稳定，因工党预计将赢得英国大选多数席位</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/pound-steady-as-labour-projected-to-win-majority-in-uk-election</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英镑保持稳定，此前一项出口民调显示，英国工党将确保其长期预测的压倒性选举胜利，而基尔·史塔默 (Keir Starmer) 有望凭借更大的经济稳定承诺成为首相。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/pound-steady-as-labour-projected-to-win-majority-in-uk-election</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 21:08:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
